import { Container, TextField } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

export default function Form() {
    return (
        <Container wid>
            <form action="" method="post">
                <TextField
                label="Entrer votre nom"
                variant="outlined"
                name="username"
                fullWidth
                />
                <TextField
                label="Entrer votre texte"
                variant="outlined"
                name="username"
                multiline
                rows={7}
                fullWidth
                />
            </form>
        </Container>
    )
}
